    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i'm not crazy... it's been happening every single time the belt is high in the sky. if its just \"psychosomatic\" why does it feel so much like a frequency? research shows satellites and arrays can use specific wavebands that mess with human perception. dont u think it's possible that even if we cant see it with normal telescopes, there's some kind of advanced tech masked as those stars?",
